---
const lineLink = 'https://line.me/R/ti/p/@782faclv';

const serviceLinks = [
  { href: '/services/eyelash', label: '超持久美睫' },
  { href: '/services/embroidery', label: '半永久紋綉' },
  { href: '/services/beauty', label: '美容美體' },
];

const quickLinks = [
  { href: '/about', label: '關於我們' },
  { href: '/portfolio', label: '作品集' },
  { href: '/blog', label: '部落格' },
  { href: '/faq', label: 'FAQ' },
];
---

<footer class="bg-[#F9F7F4]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-10">
    <!-- Main Footer Grid -->
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 lg:gap-8 mb-16"
    >
      <!-- Brand Info -->
      <div class="sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#2D2D2D] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-base font-serif"
          >
            Mi
          </div>
          <span class="font-serif text-lg tracking-wide text-[#2D2D2D]"
            >遇見Mi美學館</span
          >
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6B6B6B] mb-6 max-w-xs">
          全台北公認最持久睫毛，一站式美學服務。讓妳不用跑很多地方，也能享受全方位的美麗。
        </p>
        <a
          href={lineLink}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#06C755] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm tracking-wide transition-all duration-300 hover:brightness-110"
          data-track="line"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/line-icon.png"
            alt=""
            class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          LINE預約
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Services -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-serif text-base text-[#2D2D2D] mb-5 tracking-wide">
          服務項目
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3.5">
          {
            serviceLinks.map((link) => (
              <li>
                <a
                  href={link.href}
                  class="text-sm text-[#6B6B6B] hover:text-[#2D2D2D] transition-colors duration-300"
                >
                  {link.label}
                </a>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-serif text-base text-[#2D2D2D] mb-5 tracking-wide">
          快速連結
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3.5">
          {
            quickLinks.map((link) => (
              <li>
                <a
                  href={link.href}
                  class="text-sm text-[#6B6B6B] hover:text-[#2D2D2D] transition-colors duration-300"
                >
                  {link.label}
                </a>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-serif text-base text-[#2D2D2D] mb-5 tracking-wide">
          聯絡方式
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[#6B6B6B]">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">📍</span>
            <span>台北市大同區民生西路94號2樓<br />（雙連站1號出口30秒）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0">📞</span>
            <span>0989-260-867</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">⏰</span>
            <span
              >週一至週日 11:00-20:00<br />（完全預約制）</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div
      class="border-t border-[#E8DFD0] pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4"
    >
      <p class="text-xs text-[#6B6B6B] tracking-wide">
        © 2025 遇見Mi美學館
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-[#6B6B6B] tracking-wide">
        統一編號認證
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
